Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------ANIME-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.79,0:00:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是小心點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫的是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是檸檬？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檸檬的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這樣解釋就行了嗎  望月同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來這個檸檬就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不符合教學的主旨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是以後這樣的東西只限在美術部內部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣完成這幅畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡蒙克嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}愛德華·蒙克：挪威畫家，畫風對德國表現主義起到了重要影響，代表作有《吶喊》等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望月同學和普通人畫的都不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檸檬在吶喊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  在吶喊的是這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摀住耳朵是因為被吶喊聲嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來你是美術部的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年又開始社團活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同學不參加社團活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來美術部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敕使河原同學  你又在畫什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘋果可沒有手腳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來蘋果就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:03:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我認真畫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}回答「是」才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是一點興趣也沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同學覺得三神老師怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼問我…不太好說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到蒙克的「吶喊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看的話不覺得很可怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會感到不安嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安嗎…說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會感到不安也是無可奈何的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能引出這種心境的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為讓你不安所以喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算裝作看不見也沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  榊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在討論三神老師的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也算我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  我們在討論更黑暗一點的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  黑暗的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於籠罩世界的不安感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敕使河原同學有感覺過不安嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到升到三年級
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻偏偏被分到這個被詛咒的三班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  榊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天就想告訴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說下去就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  我有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  榊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個人沒有阻止你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幅畫是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以誰為原型的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說是你想像的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩者…都有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後還要給她畫上一對巨大的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在雨中做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不討厭雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡的是冬天冰冷的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種幾乎快化作雪的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的左眼怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在醫院見到的時候就一直戴著眼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不想說的話不用勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該回去上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新面孔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是三年三班的榊原
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛轉學過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是館長千曳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想來的話以後再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  現在快點離開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小憐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小憐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千曳先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是那個房間的主人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有那種感覺呢  那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不親切  總是穿著黑衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生一般都覺得他有點陰森
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有對你說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二號圖書室以前就在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過成為二號是應該在新校舍建成後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  恒一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打算參加社團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來今天被邀請要不要加入美術部了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡美術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不怎麼擅長畫畫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此還…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事我還沒和別人說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話  我想考一個美術系的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  這可是第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想試試雕刻和造型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有點不自量力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先你父親一定會反對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算你畢業了  也未必能找到相應的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也要看你的才能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕沒有好運的話是沒戲的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想的話就去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事在做之前就放棄的話就太遜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這很重要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:10:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自己看來是酷還是遜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉呢  白天太忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎  在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:11:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  最近在讀什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野小姐推薦給我的John  Saul的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs15}John Saul：美國懸疑恐怖小說作家，暢銷代表作有《Suffer the Children》，《The Blackstone Chronicles》等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我這邊的同事也去看看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你不是說這事來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事想要問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上週一是不是有個女生在這醫院去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上週一？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你還在住院的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…只是有點在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來事出有因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我負責的病人裡應該沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  還有另一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天你有在醫院裡看到一個穿著校服的女生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是女生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深藍色的上衣  短髮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左眼還戴著眼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼罩？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是眼科的病人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說去世的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說去世的是一個年輕的病人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫你查一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是隨口問問的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問到什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會用手機聯繫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是我提出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當作是同好的好意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你好像也有你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過下次要告訴我理由哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎  恐怖少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如大家所知道的  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「俳句」是以「五七五」十七個音節構成的定型詩中的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「俳句」這個詞也算是比較新的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約一百年前  被正岡子規所命名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前  人們稱之為「徘諧」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成俳句有三個要點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要回家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我來一下    
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  你是在夜見山的醫院出生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像馬上就回東京了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後就一直在東京？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有回來探過親嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親生下我後很快就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就沒怎麼回來過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要問這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得在哪裡見過你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認錯人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想確認的也包括那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  不是說你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法清楚地想起來  自己不爭氣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤澤同學  別想得太多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是對策組成員的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不好好做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對策組成員是做什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:15:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說  為了保護同學而制定方案並予以執行的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護？制定方案和執行？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恒一同學還沒有搞清在三班所發生的事情  以及班上制定的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤澤同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只休息了一天就給我搞成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜見黃昏下  虛無蒼之瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}請進吧  ——工房M
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原君？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你跟我說的事  已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是一名初中女生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是獨生女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母傷心欲絕  現場一片混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字呢  那女生叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不太確定…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:17:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去世的人叫「Misaki」或是「Masaki」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…類似的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從別人那兒聽到的  不知道是否準確…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  年輕的男生可不多見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是客人嗎？還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…這裡是店鋪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是中學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  夜見北的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  收你半價就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是人偶店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有拿來賣的  不過可不是中學生能買得起的價位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢  請你好好觀賞一番
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有其他客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要的話  還可以給你泡杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  不過茶就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請慢慢觀賞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}樓下展區由此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴…為什麼會在這…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你不討厭這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是為了嚇你才躲起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是你碰巧來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得很像我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有一半
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還只是一半以下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我並不討厭這裡  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你又為什麼  榊原同學又為什麼在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個因為…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便走走…那個…還沒有習慣小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就對偶然找到的這裡產生了興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:22:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人覺得這裡的人偶很噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同學不這麼認為呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.79,0:22:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡的是她們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們顯現出非常平靜的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明身體相連  還顯得如此平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不可思議了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為身體相連才能如此平靜…不是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.18,0:22:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是說身體互不相連而顯得平靜的話  還顯得正常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.82,0:22:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看看吧…  這眼罩之下
